data.description: Beautiful newly renovated 2 story home with 2 car garage, Lots of updates including 2020 Basement waterproofing system with battery backup, new roof & gutters, privacy fence, light fixtures and some flooring etc. 2023 french doors, custom kitchen with custom cabinetry and quartz countertops , upstairs carpeting, paint etc. additional upgrades the house also has a whole house HEPA filtration system, whole house vacuum system, whole house water filtration system and dual HVAC systems to climate control each floor to you comfort zone way too much to list call your agent and schedule your showing today.
